\u00edn | 29 2. \u00c9tat des connaissances 3.2. Territoires des rapaces Le travail de terrain entrepris en 2019 a permis l\u2019identification de 766 territoires de rapaces rupicoles, dont 712 correspondant avec certitude aux esp\u00e8ces cibles du Programme de d\u00e9nombrement des rapaces. Dans 54 territoires, l\u2019esp\u00e8ce n\u2019a pas pu \u00eatre d\u00e9termin\u00e9e ou il s\u2019agit d\u2019autres esp\u00e8ces d\u2019oiseaux (hors du groupe des esp\u00e8ces cibles).", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e9600837-64f3-436a-ab63-9f4fd16b465f": {"__data__": {"id_": "e9600837-64f3-436a-ab63-9f4fd16b465f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/premier-denombrement-national-des-rapaces-rupicoles-diurnes-du-maroc", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Premier d\u00e9nombrement national des rapaces rupicoles diurnes du Maroc", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/premier-denombrement-national-des-rapaces-rupicoles-diurnes-du-maroc", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "930b4a10a4c42257d4b1d93f18f13af25112c60eb5da68555fa81e275887c4ba"}, "2": {"node_id": "f19d2e13-a8f1-478a-bb9b-22d41bfec108", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/premier-denombrement-national-des-rapaces-rupicoles-diurnes-du-maroc", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Typ