ise/premier-denombrement-national-des-rapaces-rupicoles-diurnes-du-maroc", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "ae926f1f32862df67e115dc9cb1e8f8f974d7aeb3d21c76f1d43515b2d57f65d"}, "2": {"node_id": "d5a6b9b2-f22e-410a-8eed-2d9afffbe9a0", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/premier-denombrement-national-des-rapaces-rupicoles-diurnes-du-maroc", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "b4578daa5698bf0cb963a8bd28f1f23468f9698ba9b4bc415ed6e211acb1036c"}, "3": {"node_id": "8cce75d9-2961-46d7-b62c-66f0de8b0801", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/fr/resources/litterature-grise/premier-denombrement-national-des-rapaces-rupicoles-diurnes-du-maroc", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "41be8b44ccac620d7a236228c2353d820b436d52cf8c351b9a1f3cb3caab444b"}}, "hash": "812348c38f2e1bc83adc03323432dbaa606bf197d4d8057ff9bfbe2f88d19d1d", "text": "Nid ancien de Gypa\u00e8te barbu dans la r\u00e9gion de Guelmin-Oued Noun \u00a9 Justo Mart\u00edn Faucon lanier adulte \u00a9 Fondation Migres Nid occup\u00e9 dans une falaise, province de Figuig \u00a9 Karim Benaddou L\u2019\u00e9quipe de l\u2019une des missions, dans l\u2019Oriental marocain \u00a9 Helena Clavero/UICN Buse f\u00e9roce dans son nid, Agadir Ida-Outanane \u00a9 Ali Irizi/ASARA Localisation d\u2019un point de mortalit\u00e9 des rapaces par \u00e9lectrocution dans la r\u00e9gion de Guelmim-Oued Noun \u00a9 \u00cd\u00f1igo Fajardo/MAEPDD Parcours d\u2019une ligne \u00e9lectrique pour rep\u00e9rer des \u00e9ventuels cas d\u2019\u00e9lectrocution et pour \u00e9valuer les pyl\u00f4nes, province de Tan-Tan \u00